### School Rules

* 3 absents in one month is automatically dropped in all the subjects taken.

* If you got exams or other things to do tell the teacher immediately so you may be excused.

* Grading is very easy to understand it is only passed or failed.

* You'll get a certificate when you passed all the topics and the teacher is satisfied with your performance.

* You can ask the teacher to repeat the topic again and again until you learned it well.

* You can request a new subject and it will be added when the teacher is available.

* You can take any time from MON to SUN between 7am to 11am if it is available but maximum of 3hrs per subject only.

* You can only take 3 subjects simultaneously.

* You can only take 3 timeslots per month.

* If you want to dropped the subject just tell it immediately

* If you are dropped you can enroll again next month.

* Fifteen minutes late is considered an absent.

* You cannot take the same subject on the same day.

* Settle your errands before/after the class so there is no interruptions.

* If there is free time you can ask the teacher for consultation.

* All of this are for free we do not ask for any fee but donations are allowed.



